from.S: lineup.schedule s left join games.metadata g on s.game_id = g.game_id left join report.exp_access_rules a on a.level = coalesce(a.level, s.level_name) and s.location_id = coalesce(a.location, s.location_id) and cast(left(s.local_time_string,4) as integer)=coalesce(a.season, cast(left(s.local_time_string,4) as integer)) and s.home_team_id = coalesce(a.team, s.home_team_id)

group_by.S: a.org, s.game_id, g.game_reference, s.location_id, s.level_name, s.local_time_string, a.exception, a.access_start, a.access_end, s.game_state, s.home_team_name

select.S: distinct concat(a.org, s.game_id) as orggame, a.org, s.game_id, s.location_id, s.level_name, s.local_time_string, g.game_reference, a.access_start, a.access_end, a.exception, s.game_state, s.home_team_name, getdate() as date_processed

where.S: a.season = 2019 and s.local_time_string like '2019%' and (s.local_time_string > a.access_start or a.access_start is null) and (s.local_time_string < a.access_end or a.access_end is null) and a.exception = true and s.level_name <> 'MLB'
